employment-contract-v1.content:
This Employment Contract is entered into as of {{issueDate}} by and between:

1. {{employer.name}}, {{#if employer.partyType=='company'}}holding license no. {{employer.license}}{{/if}}{{#if employer.partyType=='individual'}}holding Civil ID No. {{employer.civilId}}{{/if}}, with address at: {{employer.address.building}}, {{employer.address.street}}, Block {{employer.address.block}}, {{employer.address.country}}, phone number {{employer.phone.countryCode}}-{{employer.phone.number}} (hereinafter referred to as the "Employer").
2. {{employee.name}}, holding Civil ID No. {{employee.civilId}}, with address at: {{employee.address.building}}, {{employee.address.street}}, Block {{employee.address.block}}, {{employee.address.country}}, phone number {{employee.phone.countryCode}}-{{employee.phone.number}} (hereinafter referred to as the "Employee").

The Employer agrees to employ the Employee, and the Employee agrees to work for the Employer in the position of {{jobTitle}}, commencing on {{startDate}}.

ARTICLE (1): DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES
The Employee shall be responsible for performing the following duties and responsibilities:
{{serviceDescription}}

ARTICLE (2): SALARY
The Employer agrees to pay the Employee a monthly salary of {{salary}}.

ARTICLE (3): PROBATION PERIOD
The Employee will be subject to a probation period of {{probationPeriod}} months, starting from the commencement date.

ARTICLE (4): GOVERNING LAW
This contract shall be governed by the applicable labor laws of the state.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, the parties have executed this Contract.

